                Mindware has been successfully causing organizational alignment for over 
                two decades. Working with diverse clients across industries, we know that 
                our unique transformational training approach delivers the desirable results 
                our clients are looking to accomplish.
              </p>
              
              <div class="performance-cta">
                <a href="/about" class="secondary-button">Learn More About Us</a>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Right: Graph -->
            <div class="performance-graph">
              
              <div class="svg-graph-wrapper">
                <!-- Logo Overlay -->
                <div class="logo-overlay">
                  <Image src={logo} alt="Mindware Logo" class="graph-logo-img" />
                  <span class="graph-logo-text">Effect</span>
                </div>

                <svg viewBox="0 0 400 250" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" class="main-chart-svg">
                  <!-- Desirable Curve -->
                  <path d="M20,200 Q200,180 390,50" 
                        fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="4" stroke-dasharray="10,10" />
                  
                  <!-- Predictable Curve -->
                  <path d="M20,200 L390,180" 
                        fill="none" stroke="white" stroke-width="4" stroke-dasharray="10,10" opacity="0.6" />

                  <!-- Start Dots -->
                  <circle cx="20" cy="200" r="10" fill="#EAD01F" />
                  
                  <!-- End Dots -->
                  <circle cx="390" cy="50" r="10" fill="#EAD01F" />
                  <circle cx="390" cy="180" r="10" fill="#EAD01F" />

                  <!-- Text Labels -->
                  <text x="190" y="80" fill="white" font-weight="bold" font-family="sans-serif" font-size="14">DESIRABLE</text>
